Parliament, Monday, 29 October 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Energy will tomorrow host a roundtable discussion on the draft Integrated Resource Plan 2018 (IRP). The decision to host a roundtable discussion is informed by the submissions received during the public hearings on the IRP. The roundtable discussion will assist the committee in solidifying the different views that came out during the public hearings that were conducted by the committee. Details of the roundtable discussion are as follows: Date: Tuesday, 30 October 2018
	Time: 10 am
	Venue: Committee Room V454, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8203 
	Cell: 081 497 4694
